{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"824a8d3e38","title":"毛泽东关于审阅黄炎培在上海工商界的讲话稿的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"400af785be","index":0,"year":1954,"month":3,"day":12,"articleId":"824a8d3e38"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"5611b19350","type":"title","text":"毛泽东关于审阅黄炎培在上海工商界的讲话稿的信","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"824a8d3e38"},{"id":"208cffcd5c","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"824a8d3e38"},{"id":"bd7124eaa0","type":"subtitle","text":"一","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"824a8d3e38"},{"id":"90291bb067","type":"appellation","text":"黄副总理：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"824a8d3e38"},{"id":"6fb9132c41","type":"paragraph","text":"三月八日惠书阅悉。附件已付周总理李维汉部长斟酌奉告。“人们”是指资产阶级和民主党派，不包括地主阶级和官僚资产阶级，即不是“包括一切的”。“无痛分娩法”一词最好不写在印刷品上，因实际上那些不甚觉悟的人们总会觉得有些痛苦的。支票开得多了，可能引起幻想，而不去加重教育和学习，不去提高政治觉悟，结果感觉痛苦的人就会对我们不满。尚请斟酌。敬颂大安","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"824a8d3e38"},{"id":"b4a9685580","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东一九五四年三月十二日于杭州","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"824a8d3e38"},{"id":"d41045319e","type":"subtitle","text":"二","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"824a8d3e38"},{"id":"602bc47fd2","type":"appellation","text":"恩来","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"824a8d3e38"},{"id":"9d8e9543c8","type":"paragraph","text":"同志：","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"824a8d3e38"},{"id":"a68327fc7c","type":"appellation","text":"维汉","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"824a8d3e38"},{"id":"435df78982","type":"paragraph","text":"此件请审阅斟酌，并告黄副总理。“阶级消灭，个人愉快”似以改为“阶级消灭，个人存在”为适宜，亦可告以非正式发表的谈话不要他在印刷品中引用，请酌。如他的讲演不登报，又碍难修改，听其引用亦无不可。他所谓“无痛分娩法”亦不甚妥当，只作印刷品不登报，亦可不改。末了引我的话之后他说“人们”“是包括一切的”，我已复告他不是包括一切的，地主阶级和官僚资产阶级不包括在内。我复黄信只说这一点和批评无痛分娩法一点，此外说他的信已付你们二位斟酌告他。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"824a8d3e38"},{"id":"547d7f07f6","type":"appellation","text":"敬礼！","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"824a8d3e38"},{"id":"9d853a97bf","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东一九五四年三月十二日","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"824a8d3e38"},{"id":"90d56bc49b","type":"paragraph","text":"复黄信请阅后转交。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"824a8d3e38"}],"page":{"id":"952107a50e","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"824a8d3e38","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}